ZH: 我的气管感觉有些不适。
EN: My trachea feels a bit uncomfortable.

ZH: 他的气管受了损伤，所以他说话有些困难。
EN: His trachea is damaged, so he has difficulty speaking.

ZH: 如果呼吸不畅，可能是气管发炎了。
EN: If breathing is not smooth, it may be because the trachea is inflamed.

ZH: 声音通过气管传到喉咙。
EN: The voice travels through the trachea to the throat.

ZH: 主要的呼吸道是气管和支气管。
EN: The main respiratory tract consists of the trachea and bronchi.

ZH: 他通过手术来治疗气管狭窄。
EN: He underwent surgery to treat tracheal stenosis.

ZH: 咳嗽会导致气管受到刺激。
EN: Coughing can cause irritation to the trachea.

ZH: 她在喘息时感觉刺痛的气管。
EN: She feels a sharp pain in her trachea when gasping for breath.

ZH: 当你感到窒息时，你会立刻重视气管的功能。
EN: When you feel suffocated, you immediately pay attention to the function of your trachea.

ZH: 他的气管被异物堵塞了，需要进行紧急处理。
EN: His trachea is blocked by a foreign object and requires immediate treatment.

ZH: 深吸一口气，让空气进入你的气管。
EN: Take a deep breath and let the air enter your trachea.

ZH: 这个人的气管不够发达，所以他的声音比较低沉。
EN: This person's trachea is not well developed, so his voice is relatively deep.

ZH: 浓烟进入我的气管，我开始咳嗽。
EN: Thick smoke entered my trachea, and I started coughing.

ZH: 气管镜可以检查气管内部的情况。
EN: A bronchoscope can examine the inside of the trachea.

ZH: 她感到气管发炎时，喉咙会疼痛。
EN: When her trachea is inflamed, her throat hurts.

ZH: 我的医生建议我每天用温水漱口来保护气管。
EN: My doctor advised me to rinse my mouth with warm water every day to protect my trachea.

ZH: 寒冷的空气会对气管产生刺激。
EN: Cold air can cause irritation to the trachea.

ZH: 如果你觉得吞咽有障碍，可能是气管受伤了。
EN: If you feel difficulty swallowing, it may be because your trachea is injured.

ZH: 气管炎是指气管的感染和炎症。
EN: Tracheitis refers to infection and inflammation of the trachea.

ZH: 气管支撑着喉咙，让我们能够发声。
EN: The trachea supports the throat, allowing us to produce sound.

ZH: 烟草烟雾会对气管造成损害。
EN: Tobacco smoke can damage the trachea.
